    finding: "There are no SLOs or error budgets, so reliability is unmeasured and never prioritised until customers complain; a customer-facing SLA was breached for months with no credits issued because no one tracked it.",
    refs: [["Google SRE — SLOs & Error Budgets", "https://sre.google/sre-book/service-level-objectives/"], ["ITIL 4 — Service Level Management", "https://www.axelos.com/certifications/itil-service-management"]],
